{"tid":508733,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"攝影師拍下《高潮顏》鼓勵女性也應追求床上運動的快樂","createTime":"2017-12-24T14:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T04:12:48.000Z","uid":72478,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18d6693c386bfa4d98dda04eb341da22383ef5c0","tid":508733,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:06:44.000Z","msg":"在一場性愛中，女性得到性高潮的比例為62.9%，但男性為85.1%。攝影師Albert Pocej提出的高潮顏攝影計畫，其中一個目的就是提倡女性也應該得以沒有包袱的追求性快感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.boredpanda.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Loreta-57d250ffb5a41__880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.boredpanda.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2FLoreta-57d250ffb5a41__880.jpg&h=929c943d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男性攝影師Albert Pocej相當贊同女性性解放的主張，並用他的照相機表達立場。但是，光是想到找到願意參與的模特兒，就是這個計劃中最大的挑戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.boredpanda.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Muza-57d2510542265__880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.boredpanda.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2FMuza-57d2510542265__880.jpg&h=ad31f01e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其Albert Pocej希望他的照片能夠讓大家反思兩件事情，一個是女性其實是比男性需要更長時間才能到達性高潮，但是電影或A片裡通常卻總是以男性到達性高潮後結束。作為性事上的伴侶，我們應該鼓勵男性照顧到另一半的愉悅程度，讓雙方都能得到最大程度的歡愉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.boredpanda.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Renata-57d2510e8e0cc__880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.boredpanda.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2FRenata-57d2510e8e0cc__880.jpg&h=417e8f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n更多照片： <a href=\"https://www.boredpanda.com/female-orgasms-photography-albert-pocej/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boredpanda.com%2Ffemale-orgasms-photography-albert-pocej%2F&d=AwnFYw5fpi2uRqQmtchf6gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=03b3803f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.boredpanda.com/female-orgasms-photography-albert-pocej/</a><br />\n<br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/albertpocej/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Falbertpocej%2F&d=AwnFYw5fpi2uRqQmtchf6gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4403a4c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/albertpocej/</a><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1537478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1537478&d=AwnFYw5fpi2uRqQmtchf6gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3af1c16a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1537478</a>"},{"pid":"18567994776d5953d1c94e4bd49dc8e13b3a3c14","tid":508733,"uid":123456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"影錯左打喊路相？"},{"pid":"2fa63e54a7605b798e9fa1373348e649f2472db3","tid":508733,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:21:12.000Z","msg":"男性唔係 100% <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f7242002f5986325d1187b0b6b4ad5056e5a26","tid":508733,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T04:12:48.000Z","msg":"62 都算幾高"}]}